modName: New Armor Falmer and Forsworn Merged
summary: I merged the Falmer and forsworn Armor into one armor. This mod replaces the forsworn with this modified armor.
descriptionHtml:
The top of the Armor is from the Falmer armor and the bottom is from the Forsworn armor. I thought the combination of those leather bands around the body was quite cool and I wanted to share the joy.

The Khajiit wearing the armor in this picture has my own nudemod which is why she looks a bit different than most Khajiit :)
If you are interested in that it is also posted here on the nexus:
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2278
author: Nalim666
